      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTRO LEE (1) caught the eye with a fast early split and setting up a 5.5 lengths win at this track over 407m in 23.70. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. The one to beat again. VERACIOUS VAL (6) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Mix 5 winner three back (30.23) at Q Parklands over 520m. Can turn it around this time. BAREFOOT ROGUE (8) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 35 from 71 starts. Finished second (24.06) at this track last time making it three minors on end. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Will give a great sight again. FARMOR ROGUE (2) can find the frame without surprising.",
